{"comments":"QR Code Mask Patterns — Data module masking for optimal readability.\n\n## Purpose\n\nQR codes use one of 8 mask patterns to break up large areas of\nsame-colored modules, improving scanner reliability. Only data\nmodules are masked; function patterns (finders, timing, etc.) are not.\n\n## Mask Pattern Formulas\n\nEach mask is a function of (row, col) that returns whether to flip:\n\n- Mask 0: (row + col) mod 2 == 0\n- Mask 1: row mod 2 == 0\n- Mask 2: col mod 3 == 0\n- Mask 3: (row + col) mod 3 == 0\n- Mask 4: (floor(row/2) + floor(col/3)) mod 2 == 0\n- Mask 5: (row*col) mod 2 + (row*col) mod 3 == 0\n- Mask 6: ((row*col) mod 2 + (row*col) mod 3) mod 2 == 0\n- Mask 7: ((row+col) mod 2 + (row*col) mod 3) mod 2 == 0\n\n## Selection\n\nThe best mask is selected by evaluating penalty scores for all 8\npatterns and choosing the one with minimum penalty.\n","declarations":[{"children":[{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[81,10],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Element/Compound/QRCode/Matrix/Mask.purs","start":[81,3]},"title":"Mask0"},{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[82,10],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Element/Compound/QRCode/Matrix/Mask.purs","start":[82,3]},"title":"Mask1"},{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[83,10],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Element/Compound/QRCode/Matrix/Mask.purs","start":[83,3]},"title":"Mask2"},{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[84,10],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Element/Compound/QRCode/Matrix/Mask.purs","start":[84,3]},"title":"Mask3"},{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[85,10],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Element/Compound/QRCode/Matrix/Mask.purs","start":[85,3]},"title":"Mask4"},{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[86,10],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Element/Compound/QRCode/Matrix/Mask.purs","start":[86,3]},"title":"Mask5"},{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[87,10],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Element/Compound/QRCode/Matrix/Mask.purs","start":[87,3]},"title":"Mask6"},{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[88,10],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Element/Compound/QRCode/Matrix/Mask.purs","start":[88,3]},"title":"Mask7"},{"comments":null,"info":{"declType":"instance","dependencies":[],"type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Data","Eq"],"Eq"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Element","Compound","QRCode","Matrix","Mask"],"MaskPattern"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"sourceSpan":{"end":[90,48],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Element/Compound/QRCode/Matrix/Mask.purs","start":[90,1]},"title":"eqMaskPattern"},{"comments":null,"info":{"declType":"instance","dependencies":[],"type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Data","Ord"],"Ord"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Element","Compound","QRCode","Matrix","Mask"],"MaskPattern"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"sourceSpan":{"end":[91,50],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Element/Compound/QRCode/Matrix/Mask.purs","start":[91,1]},"title":"ordMaskPattern"},{"comments":null,"info":{"declType":"instance","dependencies":[],"type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Data","Show"],"Show"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Element","Compound","QRCode","Matrix","Mask"],"MaskPattern"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"sourceSpan":{"end":[101,23],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Element/Compound/QRCode/Matrix/Mask.purs","start":[93,1]},"title":"showMaskPattern"}],"com